headline.main: Battle-Hardened in Britain, May Prepares for Brexit Talks
headline.print_headline: Battle-Hardened in Britain, May Prepares for Brexit Talks

lead_paragraph: British Prime Minister Theresa May is unlikely to bow to political expedience in Brexit negotiations but will make up her own mind about what she believes is best and refuse to give ground - that's if past form is anything to go by.
